            Tailwind
          </span>
          <span class="skill-badge">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style="background: #f43f5e;"></span>
            Git
          </span>
          <span class="skill-badge">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style="background: #6366f1;"></span>
            Vue/Nuxt
          </span>
